snippet.title: Millennials Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready to go back to college? 
Take a look at Millennials Steam Page and wishlist us here 👉 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2103090/Millennials/ 

In Millennials you’ll create your own college freshman. Experience the hardships of college in this amusing and engaging life sim game. Study hard and party even harder. Join a fraternity to meet new interesting individuals. It is entirely up to you how your academic career will progress!👨‍🎓

Take part in many activities available on campus:
- Attend classes
- Explore the various clubs
- Support your fraternity/sorority
- Throw parties
- Meet with friends
- Deepen relationships
- Work part-time to pay tuition
- Decorate and chill out in your dorm room

Social media channels:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/frozenWay 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/FrozenWayGames
Discord: https://discord.gg/fw-official
